@startuml
title Feature 027 admin CMS sequence

actor "Контент-администратор" as Admin
actor "Редактор" as Editor
actor "Юридический reviewer" as Legal
participant "Frontend AdminCmsView" as FE
participant "Auth/RBAC context" as Auth
participant "admin-cms controller" as Controller
participant "admin-cms service" as Service
participant "admin-cms validator" as Validator
database "admin-cms storage" as DB
collections "S3/MinIO file references" as S3
participant "public-content projection" as Public

Admin -> FE: opens /admin/cms
FE -> Auth: read session permissions
Auth --> FE: ADMIN_CMS_MANAGE, ADMIN_CMS_REVIEW
FE -> Controller: GET /api/admin-cms/materials
Controller -> Service: searchMaterials(filters, actor)
Service -> DB: query materials allowed by scope
DB --> Service: material summaries
Service --> Controller: AdminCmsMaterialListResponse
Controller --> FE: 200 list

Editor -> FE: create NEWS/FAQ/DOCUMENT draft
FE -> Controller: POST /api/admin-cms/materials
Controller -> Service: createMaterial(request, actor, correlationId)
Service -> Validator: validate type, slug, blocks, SEO, document metadata
Validator --> Service: valid or mnemonic error
Service -> DB: insert material, version, blocks, seo, relations, audit
DB --> Service: persisted draft
Service --> Controller: detail + STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_CMS_MATERIAL_SAVED
Controller --> FE: 201 detail

FE -> Controller: POST /api/admin-cms/materials/{id}/preview
Controller -> Service: buildPreview(materialId, actor)
Service -> DB: read draft version and blocks
Service --> Controller: preview render model
Controller --> FE: 200 preview without publication

Editor -> FE: submit to review
FE -> Controller: POST /materials/{id}/submit-review
Controller -> Service: submitReview(materialId, actor)
Service -> Validator: validate lifecycle and required fields
Service -> DB: update status IN_REVIEW or LEGAL_REVIEW, write audit
DB --> Service: updated material
Service --> Controller: detail
Controller --> FE: 200 detail

Legal -> FE: approve legal document
FE -> Controller: POST /materials/{id}/review
Controller -> Service: applyReview(APPROVED, comment, actor)
Service -> Validator: validate reviewer scope and legal requirements
Service -> DB: insert review decision, update version APPROVED, audit
DB --> Service: approved version
Service --> Controller: STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_CMS_REVIEW_APPROVED
Controller --> FE: 200 detail

Admin -> FE: schedule or publish
FE -> Controller: POST /materials/{id}/publish
Controller -> Service: publish(materialId, publishAt, unpublishAt, actor)
Service -> Validator: validate approved version and publication window
Service -> DB: update material SCHEDULED or PUBLISHED, audit
Service -> Public: expose published render model only when active
Public --> Service: projection updated
Service --> Controller: STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_CMS_MATERIAL_PUBLISHED
Controller --> FE: 200 detail

Admin -> FE: rollback previous version
FE -> Controller: POST /materials/{id}/versions/{versionId}/rollback
Controller -> Service: rollback(materialId, versionId, actor)
Service -> DB: copy previous version to new DRAFT, audit
DB --> Service: new draft version
Service --> Controller: 201 detail
Controller --> FE: detail

Admin -> FE: open audit
FE -> Controller: GET /api/admin-cms/audit
Controller -> Service: searchAudit(filters, actor)
Service -> DB: query immutable audit events
DB --> Service: events without secrets/private paths
Service --> Controller: AdminCmsAuditResponse
Controller --> FE: 200 audit

@enduml